	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. 66. See above, on Cassius (13). It remains uncertain whether the monetalis of 78 (Crawford, RRC 1.403, no. 386) may be identified with the praetor of 66 (MRR 2.152) and candidate for the consulship of 63 (Ascon. 92C; Comm. Pet. 7).\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7570 .
